OWLS
NC Value Guide

Owls (est. August 2021) is a Neocash item value guide designed to help you (yes, you!) figure out estimated values for Neocash item trades on Neopets.com.

Owls is an unofficial page run by passionate Neopets fans. It is not affiliated with The Neopets Team, Neopets, Inc., or Neopets.com. All information contained within is subjective, based on community-reported data, and may be adjusted or removed at any time as needed.

Want to search our trade database or submit your own report to us? Join our Discord server and get acquainted with OwlBot, your friendly feathered NC-trading companion!

Support us on Ko-Fi!

Interested in joining the Owls team? Neomail or contact Kaye (catelyn_tully_stark)!








Disclaimers

  • Guides are not law and it is okay to disagree with our published guide values. Use your own discretion when negotiating trades.
  • Owls is not updated 24/7 and values or item availability may have shifted since the last update.
  • If an item is listed at 00 - 00, it means we do not currently have enough data to assign a value.
  • Owls lists the numerical values of items based on trade data reported by the community.
  • We do not update subjectively and cannot modify values without trade reports.
  • We use American MM/DD for dates.
  • Ctrl/command + F to find an item
  • Mouse Over or Select an item to see when we last updated it!
